                    "en": "Located on Lot B2.4 (03,04,05) on Vo Nguyen Giap Street (An Cu 3 Expanded Residential Area), Phuoc My Ward, Son Tra District, City. Da Nang, Glow Mabelle Hotel project is invested by Tuyet Lien Son Company Limited. This is a level 1 civil project, designed according to 4-star hotel standards. The construction scale includes 25 floors and 02 basements, with a total floor area exceeding 25,000 m2. A.S.P.T Consulting & Construction Company Limited is responsible for designing the entire mechanical and electrical system, structure as well as architecture of the project. In particular, the architectural concept was assigned to the Salvador company (Spain), which began implementing the work in January 2016. At present, the project has been completed and put into use.",
