                    "en": "Located on the Han River of Da Nang city, the Marina Cruise Restaurant project is invested and built by DHC Company. This is a special level III civil project with a complex structure, consisting of 5 floors with large spans, using pre-stressed reinforced concrete structure and designed according to an architectural model like a ship floating on the river surface. Starting from December 2013, A.S.P.T Consulting & Construction Company Limited has participated in the project with the task of undertaking the design stage for the entire structural body from the foundation up. Currently, the project has been completed and put into use.",
